bel="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770760680" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675770760680"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>A combination of elegance and purity. The Silver is a work of art made of sculpted solid silver. The&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">perfection of its polish harmonises perfectly with its sober and generous design. Its 18-carat gold nib is&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">embedded in its oval to complete its perfect aesthetic.</span></p><p><br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="2" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767638977" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675767638977" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/products/pilot-custom-enju-fountain-pen-wood" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/96e7df90-154b-4ad7-91e1-962e0a047dcc/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/FW-Double-Tile-2---Pilot-Custom-Enju.jpg" alt="Pilot Custom Enju" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1024" height="658" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770684406" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675770684406"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><a href="/products/pilot-custom-enju-fountain-pen-wood" class="">Pilot Custom Enju</a></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770879686" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675770879686"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Her body is made of precious Japanese pagoda wood, a majestic tree that symbolises the path to increased&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">awareness and perception, filled with wisdom, peace, and harmony. Featuring golden trims and a two-tone&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">18-carat gold nib (No. 15), it is of a rare and timeless elegance.</span></p><p><br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="3" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1722289179732" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1722289179732" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/pilot-justus" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/fbb7b040-be75-4b39-aaf0-99cbe7e7db37/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/FW-Double-Tile-2---Pilot-Justus.jpg" alt="Pilot Justus" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1024" height="658" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" style="" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1722289179799" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1722289179799"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><a href="/collections/pilot-justus" class="">Pilot Justus</a></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1722289179850" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1722289179850"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>A technical masterpiece that adjusts the flexibility of the nib Not only is it beautiful, with its resin body&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">discreetly machined to catch the light, it’s also intelligent, with an ingenious rotating system that adjusts&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; background-color: transparent;">the flexibility of its 14-carat gold nib to suit your mood and needs.</span></p><p><br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div data-index="4" class="item-content"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1722289181756" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1722289181756" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/collections/pilot-grance" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/5349de1c-da0b-4dcf-be85-55b7320cbd8f/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/FW-Double-Tile-4---Pilot-Grance.jpg" alt="Pilot Grance" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1024" height="658" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1024" natural-height="658" data-lg-size="2048x2048" loading="lazy"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element"